RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.Priority AS 'Priority', DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.Status AS 'Status', DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.PeerStatus AS 'Peer Status', DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.DesiredStatus AS 'Desired Status' FROM AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, Port, DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult, LldpNodeConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND LldpNodeConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.ParentHnd = LldpNodeConfig.Handle AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND LldpNodeConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) UNION SELECT ExternalDevicePort.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.Priority AS 'Priority', DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.Status AS 'Status', DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.PeerStatus AS 'Peer Status', DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.DesiredStatus AS 'Desired Status' FROM AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, ExternalDevicePort, DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult, Port, LldpNodeConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND LldpNodeConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.ParentHnd = LldpNodeConfig.Handle AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND ExternalDevicePort.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND DcbxPriorityFlowControlResult.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND LldpNodeConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId )
